This is somewhat depressing for me, as I’m working on a team with the name ‘project 2006’ :o But to be blunt I don’t think you guys will become large enough for me to worry

But yea, I don’t think the other project has a monopoly on using ‘2006’ in the name, and they definitely don’t use project (It’s just been a mixture of ‘scape’/‘rs’, and ‘2006’/‘06’ iirc)

But yea, using the name vault does seem pretty interesting too xD
